<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/728cbad6-b063-40de-b07c-4ce027f4614b> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
