<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c3dd07a8afbe337702ca353f72d6c08b>.
<#c3dd07a8afbe337702ca353f72d6c08b> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/79c2ad4f-a216-4636-9714-713adc3c3a6a>;
