}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b70bcde1cb95ee9c86fec26ef9cb3860>.
<#b70bcde1cb95ee9c86fec26ef9cb3860> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
