}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#891bca2cc18e89e8d56430d1260cd7ca>.
<#891bca2cc18e89e8d56430d1260cd7ca> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/7e881b5c-544b-4c91-a7ec-c8e2a01f6026>;
