    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/ProvenanceStatement>.
<http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U85202> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Medarbetarengagemang (HME) regional utveckling - Ledarskapsindex"@sv;
