<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#37d5ee0db19a0ae8a298b0fd6d5cdb4d>.
<#37d5ee0db19a0ae8a298b0fd6d5cdb4d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata.umea.se/api/v2/catalog/datasets/leverantorsfakturor-2020>;
