<#8af1d7e581efb5b6b4097f815b31a5ec> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/230>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-08T06:13:37.593Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
