<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#570835f76f98b9fd654f5f10ffc7f1fb>.
<#570835f76f98b9fd654f5f10ffc7f1fb> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://konsumentverket.entryscape.net/store/1/resource/255>;
